# OneRF — ecossistema e documentação

Antes de implementar ou rever código em **qualquer** repo OneRF:

1. **Docs comuns (SSOT):** [onerf-platform-docs/README.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/README.md) — ou path relativo `../../onerf-platform-docs/` no monorepo `git_onerf/`.
2. **Visão de plataforma:** [platform/PLATFORM_VISION.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/platform/PLATFORM_VISION.md)
3. **Ecossistema:** [ECOSYSTEM.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/ECOSYSTEM.md)

## Por repositório

| Repo | Docs locais | Índice produto |
|------|-------------|----------------|
| `backend` | `docs/README.md`, `context.md` | [products/backend-iot/README.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/products/backend-iot/README.md) |
| `b2b_analytics` | `docs/ENGINEERING.md` | [products/analytics/README.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/products/analytics/README.md) |
| Apps `/apps/` | README + ARCHITECTURE.md | [products/vertical-apps/README.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/products/vertical-apps/README.md) |

## Regras

- **Não duplicar** princípios de plataforma nos repos satélite — alterar em `onerf-platform-docs`.
- Contrato HTTP normativo: [platform/API_CONTRACT.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/platform/API_CONTRACT.md); OpenAPI **vivo** em cada serviço.
- Integração Backend ↔ Analytics: [platform/INTEGRATION_PATTERNS.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/platform/INTEGRATION_PATTERNS.md) + `backend/docs/INTEGRATION_ANALYTICS.md`.
- ADR-001: **sem MQTT** inter-sistema — [adr/001-no-mqtt-inter-system.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/adr/001-no-mqtt-inter-system.md).
